caption.title: Trichomonas vaginalis 30236 isolate; MIC and IC 50 after 24-hour-treatments with EOP at 25, 50, 100, 200, 300, 400, 500 μg/mL.
caption.p: Data represent mean ± standard deviation of at least three experiments, all in triplicate. Different letters indicate a significant difference (p < 0.05).
